You can Ritual Summon this card with any "Nekroz" Ritual Spell Card. Must be Ritual Summoned by using monsters other than "The Nekroz Armor of Brionac", and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. You can discard this card; add 1 "Nekroz" monster from your Deck to your hand, except "The Nekroz Armor of Brionac". You can target up to 2 monsters on the field that were Special Summoned from the Extra Deck; shuffle them into the Deck. You can only use each effect of "The Nekroz Armor of Brionac" once per turn.
